# Marker kept IN PLACE deliberately: the owner's GLOBAL ~/.claude UserPromptSubmit hook
# (auto-project-setup.sh) re-installs the generic pack whenever this marker is missing.
# Do not quarantine or delete it. Durable fix = owner removes that hook from global settings.
.claude/.auto-setup-complete
